# Template Command - Quick Reference

## Command

```bash
/template generate deal <excel.xlsx>
```

## What It Does

Converts Deal Transfer Excel files → 3 proposal files

**Input**: Deal Transfer Excel (.xlsx with S1 + S2 sheets)
**Output**: Template + Reasoning + Checklist files

## Example

```bash
/template generate deal DT_0109.xlsx
```

**Output**:
```
🎯 Template Generation Started
📁 Excel: DT_0109.xlsx
📊 Project: Leda Inio Construction

[Step 1/5] Validate Excel File [✓ COMPLETED]
[Step 2/5] Extract Deal Transfer Data [✓ COMPLETED]
[Step 3/5] Generate Template File [✓ COMPLETED]
[Step 4/5] Generate Reasoning File [✓ COMPLETED]
[Step 5/5] Generate Checklist File [✓ COMPLETED]

✅ Complete!
Output: ./output/Leda_Inio_20250126_163030/
